author: Brenda Goh
title: A city traumatized: Lockdown easing, Wuhan residents fret over future
description: Li Xiaoli has been hard at work in recent days at the car dealership she owns in Wuhan, making sure she has enough sanitizer and protective gear for the company's long-awaited reopening.
